data.description: $5000 towards closing!! Cozy 3BR/2Bath Ranch-style home located just outside the city limits and in highly preferred Northern School District! Located on 2.25 acres this home offers large fenced backyard, spacious landscaped front yard, covered rocking chair front porch (perfect for enjoying neighbors horse farm), deck in back for your morning coffee or evening relaxing, spacious garage. and backs up to state protected Haw River State Park land. Lots of updates: Roof (2017), HVAC (2018), Hot water heater (2021), garage door/opener (2023), and updated landscaping. Newly installed generator access plug and manuel switch. Seller is offering $5000 for paint, flooring, etc. allowance to buyer at closing with adequate offer! Do not miss out on this location, school district, acreage, and county taxes!! Short drive to Greensboro, Summerfield, Reidsville, and shopping/restaurants just down the road.  Schedule your showing soon!! See Agent Remarks for more details....
